<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Foil2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Foil,</orth> subst. that on which a jewel is placed to set it off; and hence anything serving to give lustre to another thing: <bibl n="shak. lc 153" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 153</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.266" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 266</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.239" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 239</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.250" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 250</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.266" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 266</bibl>.
